# Experiment 01 ŌĆö Baseline TFNO2D: Complete Configuration & Methods Reference

> **Scope**: This document covers **only** the baseline TFNO2D run (`exp_01_baseline.ipynb`), excluding UNet and ResidualSTUNet architectures.

