## 1. Features & Input Channels

| Group | Features | Count |
|-------|----------|-------|
| **Target** | [cpm25](file:///home/raj/Documents/CODING/Hackathon/ANRF_TEST/ANRF_AISEHack_Code/Ronit/src/data.py#103-105) | 1 |
